- cs.SOC (Computational Social Science) is another possible category as the paper explores the underlying networking needs in different social networks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper mentions the potential advancement in designing graph generation models and recommender systems. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper discusses the impact of structural diversity on link existence in networks.
